criteria.driver_alignment:
Reflect — provides explicit recommendations on optimal capital structure and trade-offs;  
Evolve — quantified a financing scenario (debt issuance) and its WACC impact to inform the recommendation;  
Discover/Represent — tied the recommendation back to the original goal of determining cost of capital and WACC components.

Implement — computed the WACC impact of a specific debt issuance scenario;  
Evolve/Reflect — interpreted trade-offs (tax shield benefits vs. financial distress) and made a financing recommendation;  
Discover/Represent — framed capital-structure considerations within the WACC/hurdle-rate objective.
